subject: Soccer
organizations: United States Women's National Soccer Team
lead_paragraph: Ugo Ihemelu scored in the 36th minute to lift F.C. Dallas to a 1-0 victory over El Salvador’s Alianza F.C. in the second leg of their Concacaf Champions League preliminary round match.
